---

 <section class="cities-section">
    <div class="cities-container">
        <header class="cities-header">
        <h2>Cities to Explore in Iran</h2>
        </header>

        <!-- GROUP 1 - WHITE -->
        <div class="city-group city-group--light">
        <div class="cities-grid">
            <!-- Column 1 -->
            <div class="city-column">
            <article class="city-item">
                <div class="city-img">
                <img
                    src="/src/images/cities/mashhad.jpeg"
                    alt="Mashhad city view"
                />
                </div>
                <div class="city-text">
                <h3>Mashhad</h3>
                <p>
                    Home to the holy shrine of Imam Reza (AS), Mashhad is one
                    of the most important pilgrimage destinations in the
                    Islamic world, surrounded by bazaars and spiritual energy.
                </p>
                </div>
            </article>

            <article class="city-item">
                <div class="city-img">
                <img
                    src="/src/images/cities/qom.png"
                    alt="Qum shrine and courtyard"
                />
                </div>
                <div class="city-text">
                <h3>Qum</h3>
                <p>
                    A major religious center with seminaries, shrines, and
                    traditional streets where history, scholarship, and faith
                    come together.
                </p>
                </div>
            </article>
            </div>

            <!-- Column 2 -->
            <div class="city-column">
            <article class="city-item">
                <div class="city-img">
                <img
                    src="/src/images/cities/tehran.webp"
                    alt="Tehran skyline and mountains"
                />
                </div>
                <div class="city-text">
                <h3>Tehran</h3>
                <p>
                    Iran’s lively capital blends museums, modern cafés, and
                    bazaars with views of the Alborz mountains and a dynamic
                    urban culture.
                </p>
                </div>
            </article>

            <article class="city-item">
                <div class="city-img">
                <img
                    src="/src/images/cities/isfahan.jpg"
                    alt="Isfahan Naqsh-e Jahan square"
                />
                </div>
                <div class="city-text">
                <h3>Isfahan</h3>
                <p>
                    Famous for its turquoise domes, historic bridges, and
                    grand squares, Isfahan is often called “half the world”
                    for its beauty and heritage.
                </p>
                </div>
            </article>
            </div>
        </div>
        </div>

        <!-- GROUP 2 - BEIGE -->
        <div class="city-group city-group--beige">
        <div class="cities-grid">
            <!-- Column 1 -->
            <div class="city-column">
            <article class="city-item">
                <div class="city-img">
                <img
                    src="/src/images/cities/kashan.jpg"
                    alt="Kashan traditional house"
                />
                </div>
                <div class="city-text">
                <h3>Kashan</h3>
                <p>
                    A desert-edge city known for elegant historic houses,
                    traditional baths, and rosewater fragrance during spring.
                </p>
                </div>
            </article>

            <article class="city-item">
                <div class="city-img">
                <img src="/src/images/cities/yazd.jpg" alt="Yazd windcatchers" />
                </div>
                <div class="city-text">
                <h3>Yazd</h3>
                <p>
                    Adobe alleys, windcatchers, and Zoroastrian heritage make
                    this desert city feel timeless under glowing desert skies.
                </p>
                </div>
            </article>
            </div>

            <!-- Column 2 -->
            <div class="city-column">
            <article class="city-item">
                <div class="city-img">
                <img
                    src="/src/images/cities/shiraz.jpg"
                    alt="Shiraz Nasir al-Mulk mosque"
                />
                </div>
                <div class="city-text">
                <h3>Shiraz</h3>
                <p>
                    Known for poetry, gardens, and nearby Persepolis, Shiraz
                    captures the romantic, artistic spirit of Iran.
                </p>
                </div>
            </article>

            <article class="city-item">
                <div class="city-img">
                <img
                    src="/src/images/cities/tabriz.jpg"
                    alt="Tabriz historic bazaar"
                />
                </div>
                <div class="city-text">
                <h3>Tabriz</h3>
                <p>
                    Once a key Silk Road hub, Tabriz offers a UNESCO-listed
                    bazaar, rich Azeri culture, and mountain landscapes.
                </p>
                </div>
            </article>
            </div>
        </div>
        </div>

        <!-- GROUP 3 - WHITE -->
        <div class="city-group city-group--light">
        <div class="cities-grid">
            <!-- Column 1 -->
            <div class="city-column">
            <article class="city-item">
                <div class="city-img">
                <img
                    src="/src/images/cities/kerman.jpg"
                    alt="Kerman desert and fort"
                />
                </div>
                <div class="city-text">
                <h3>Kerman</h3>
                <p>
                    Gateway to the Lut Desert and historic citadels, Kerman
                    mixes desert adventure with centuries of trading history.
                </p>
                </div>
            </article>

            <article class="city-item">
                <div class="city-img">
                <img
                    src="/src/images/cities/hamedan.jpeg"
                    alt="Hamedan city view"
                />
                </div>
                <div class="city-text">
                <h3>Hamedan</h3>
                <p>
                    One of Iran’s oldest cities, associated with ancient
                    Ecbatana and surrounded by fresh mountain air.
                </p>
                </div>
            </article>
            </div>

            <!-- Column 2 -->
            <div class="city-column">
            <article class="city-item">
                <div class="city-img">
                <img
                    src="/src/images/cities/rasht.jpg"
                    alt="Rasht green landscape"
                />
                </div>
                <div class="city-text">
                <h3>Rasht</h3>
                <p>
                    A culinary capital in the lush north, Rasht offers vibrant
                    food culture and easy access to forests and the Caspian.
                </p>
                </div>
            </article>

            <article class="city-item">
                <div class="city-img">
                <img
                    src="/src/images/cities/qazvin.jpg"
                    alt="Qazvin historic gate"
                />
                </div>
                <div class="city-text">
                <h3>Qazvin</h3>
                <p>
                    A former royal capital with caravanserais, calligraphy
                    heritage, and quick access to Alamut Valley.
                </p>
                </div>
            </article>
            </div>
        </div>
        </div>

        <!-- GROUP 4 - BEIGE -->
        <div class="city-group city-group--beige">
        <div class="cities-grid">
            <!-- Column 1 -->
            <div class="city-column">
            <article class="city-item">
                <div class="city-img">
                <img
                    src="/src/images/cities/ramsar.jpg"
                    alt="Ramsar sea and forest"
                />
                </div>
                <div class="city-text">
                <h3>Ramsar</h3>
                <p>
                    Where the Caspian Sea meets forested mountains, Ramsar is
                    perfect for cable cars, hot springs, and sea views.
                </p>
                </div>
            </article>

            <article class="city-item">
                <div class="city-img">
                <img
                    src="/src/images/cities/bandar_abbas.jpg"
                    alt="Bandar Abbas port and coast"
                />
                </div>
                <div class="city-text">
                <h3>Bandar Abbas</h3>
                <p>
                    A bustling port city on the Persian Gulf with coastal
                    promenades and access to southern islands.
                </p>
                </div>
            </article>
            </div>

            <!-- Column 2 -->
            <div class="city-column">
            <article class="city-item">
                <div class="city-img">
                <img
                    src="/src/images/cities/qeshm.jpg"
                    alt="Qeshm island landscapes"
                />
                </div>
                <div class="city-text">
                <h3>Qeshm</h3>
                <p>
                    Known for dramatic rock formations, mangrove forests, and
                    geosites, Qeshm is an eco-adventurer’s paradise.
                </p>
                </div>
            </article>

            <article class="city-item">
                <div class="city-img">
                <img
                    src="/src/images/cities/qish.jpg"
                    alt="Kish island coastline"
                />
                </div>
                <div class="city-text">
                <h3>Kish</h3>
                <p>
                    A relaxed island escape with clear waters, coral beaches,
                    and cycling paths along the shoreline.
                </p>
                </div>
            </article>
            </div>
        </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    </section>